\begin_layout Standard
The Chinese virus was previously unknown, yet it was clear that eventually
 it would spread to every aprt of the world.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
China declared that the virus would not spread otherwise, but at the end
 it was not the case and a pandemic began.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Lockdowns were initiated around the world and the medical personell panicked
 as it was questionable whether the health systems would be able to accommodate
